NEW PODCAST OUT (315)!

In this episode I interview UCLA doctoral student and mother of an autistic child on:

🧠Racial disparities in American healthcare

🧠Stephanie’s own experiences as a mother to a child with autism 

🧠How the autism label can fail many people

🧠Advice for parents with autistic children 

And more!
